<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/DimensionlessUnit> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  <p>A <em>Dimensionless Unit</em> is a quantity for which all the exponents of the factors corresponding to the base quantities in its quantity dimension are zero.\n  </p>"^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
