<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Quantity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Quantifiable> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Quantity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Verifiable> .
