<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityKindDimensionVector_Imperial> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityKindDimensionVector_Imperial> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
