<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ScalarDataItem> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  <p>A <em>Data Item</em> holds a value that is compliant with a specified <em>Datatype</em>.\n  </p>"^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ScalarDataItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ScalarDataItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Scalar Data Item"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ScalarDataItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Concept> .
