<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/applicableSIUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "applicable SI unit"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/applicableSIUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Unit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/applicableSIUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/applicableUnit> .
