<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/applicableSystem> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  This property relates a unit of measure with a unit system that may or may not define the unit,\n   but within which the unit is compatible.\n  "^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/applicableSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/applicableSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "applicable system"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/applicableSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/SystemOfUnits> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/applicableUSCustomaryUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/applicableUSCustomaryUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
