<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseDimensionEnumeration> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseDimensionEnumeration> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This property associates a system of quantities with an enumeration that enumerates the base dimensions of the system in canonical order."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseDimensionEnumeration> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseDimensionEnumeration> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "base dimension enumeration"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseDimensionEnumeration> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Enumeration> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseUnitOfSystem> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  This property relates a unit of measure to the system of units in which it is defined as a base unit for the system. \n  The base units of a system are used to define the derived units of the system by expressing the derived units as products of the base units raised to a rational power.\n  "^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasBaseUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is base unit of system"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/definedUnitOfSystem> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/belongsToSystemOfQuantities> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/belongsToSystemOfQuantities> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/belongsToSystemOfQuantities> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "belongs to system of quantities"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/belongsToSystemOfQuantities> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/SystemOfQuantityKinds> .
