<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/definedUnitOfSystem> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This property relates a unit of measure with the unit system that defines the unit."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/definedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDefinedUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/definedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/definedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "defined unit of system"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/definedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/SystemOfUnits> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/definedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/isUnitOfSystem> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This property relates a unit of measure to the unit system in which the unit is derived from the system's base units with a proportionality constant of one."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedCoherentUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is coherent derived unit of system"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/SystemOfUnits> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/definedUnitOfSystem> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedUnitOfSystem> .
