<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedNonCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  This property relates a unit of measure to the unit system in which the unit is derived from the system's\n   base units without proportionality constant of one.\n  "^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedNonCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedNonCoherentUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedNonCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedNonCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is non-coherent derived unit of system"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedNonCoherentUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedUnitOfSystem> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedUnitOfSystem> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  This property relates a unit of measure to the system of units in which it is defined as a derived unit. \n  That is, the derived unit is defined as a product of the base units for the system raised to some rational power.\n  "^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is derived unit of system"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/SystemOfUnits> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/isUnitOfSystem> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/dimensionInverse> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/dimensionInverse> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#InverseFunctionalProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/dimensionInverse> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
