<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/dimensionVectorForSI> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/dimensionVectorForSI> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/dimensionVectorForSI> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/dimensionVectorForSI> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "dimension vector for SI"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/dimensionVectorForSI> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityKindDimensionVector_SI> .
