<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasBaseQuantityKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityKind> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasBaseQuantityKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasQuantityKind> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasBaseUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasBaseUnit> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  This property relates a system of units to a base unit defined within the system.\n  The base units of a system are used to define the derived units of the system by expressing\n   the derived units as products of the base units raised to a rational power.\n  "^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasBaseUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/baseUnitOfSystem> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasBaseUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasBaseUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "base unit"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasBaseUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Unit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasBaseUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasCoherentUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasCoherentUnit> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  A coherent unit of measurement for a unit system is a defined unit that may be expressed as a product of powers\n   of the system's base units with the proportionality factor of one.\n  "^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "coherent unit"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Unit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDefinedUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDefinedUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDefinedUnit> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This property relates a unit system with a unit of measure that is defined by the system."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDefinedUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDefinedUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "defined unit"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDefinedUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Unit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDefinedUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedCoherentUnitOfSystem> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "derived coherent unit"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Unit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasCoherentUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedNonCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedNonCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedNonCoherentUnitOfSystem> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedNonCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedNonCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has coherent derived unit"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedNonCoherentUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedUnit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedUnit> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  This property relates a system of units to a unit of measure that is defined within the system in terms\n   of the base units for the system. \n  That is, the derived unit is defined as a product of the base units for the system raised to some rational power.\n  "^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/derivedUnitOfSystem> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "derived unit"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDerivedUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Unit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDimensionVector> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDimensionVector> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDimensionVector> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has dimension vector"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasDimensionVector> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityKindDimensionVector> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasFactorUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasFactorUnit> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This property relates a derived unit to one of its constituent factor units"^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasFactorUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasFactorUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasFactorUnit"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasQuantityKind> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasQuantityKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasQuantityKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has quantity kind"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasQuantityKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityKind> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasReciprocalUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasReciprocalUnit> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Used to relate a unit to its reciprocal unit."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasReciprocalUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasReciprocalUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has reciprocal unit"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasReciprocalUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Unit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasReferenceQuantityKind> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasReferenceQuantityKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasReferenceQuantityKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has reference quantity kind"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasReferenceQuantityKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityKind> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasRule> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasRule> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasRule> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has rule"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasRule> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Rule> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnit> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  <p>This property relates a factor unit to its unit or system of units with a unit of measure that is either:\n  </p>\n  <dl>\n  <dd>a) defined by the system,</dd>\n  <dd>b) accepted for use by the system and is convertible to a unit of equivalent dimension that is defined by the system,</dd>\n  <dd>c) a reference to the unit of measure of a quantity (variable or constant) of interest.</dd>\n  </dl>\n  <p>Systems of units may distinguish between base and derived units.\n  Base units are the units which measure the base quantities for the corresponding system of quantities. \n  The base units are used to define units for all other quantities as products of powers of the base units. \n  Such units are called derived units for the system. \n  </p>"^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has unit"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Unit> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnitSystem> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnitSystem> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnitSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnitSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has unit system"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/hasUnitSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/SystemOfUnits> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/isUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/isUnitOfSystem> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\n  This property relates a unit of measure with a system of units that either a) defines the unit\n   or b) allows the unit to be used within the system.\n  "^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/isUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/isUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is unit of system"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/isUnitOfSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/SystemOfUnits> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/permissibleMaths> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/permissibleMaths> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/permissibleMaths> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "permissible maths"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/permissibleMaths> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/MathsFunctionType> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/permissibleTransformation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/permissibleTransformation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/permissibleTransformation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "permissible transformation"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/permissibleTransformation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/TransformType> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/prefix> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/prefix> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Associates a unit with the appropriate prefix, if any."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/prefix> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/prefix> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "prefix"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/prefix> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Prefix> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/qkdvDenominator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/qkdvDenominator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/qkdvDenominator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/qkdvDenominator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "denominator dimension vector"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/qkdvDenominator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityKindDimensionVector> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/qkdvNumerator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/qkdvNumerator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/qkdvNumerator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/qkdvNumerator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "numerator dimension vector"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/qkdvNumerator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityKindDimensionVector> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantity> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "a property to relate an observable thing with a quantity (qud:Quantity)"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "quantity"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/Quantity> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantityValue> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantityValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantityValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "quantity value"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/quantityValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityValue> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ruleType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ruleType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ruleType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "rule type"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ruleType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/RuleType> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/scaleType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/scaleType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/scaleType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/scaleType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "scale type"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/scaleType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ScaleType> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/scalingOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/scalingOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/scalingOf> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This property relates a unit that is scaled to the base unit that its qudt:conversionMultiplier converts it to"^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/scalingOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
