<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/currencyCode> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Alphabetic Currency Code as defined by ISO 4217. For example, the currency code for the US dollar is USD."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/currencyCode> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
