<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/isoNormativeReference> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/isoNormativeReference> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/normativeReference> .
