<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/relativeStandardUncertainty> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The relative standard uncertainty of a measurement is the (absolute) standard uncertainty divided by the magnitude of the exact value."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
