<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/standardUncertaintySN> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/standardUncertaintySN> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The standard uncertainty of a quantity is the estimated standard deviation of the mean taken from a series of measurements."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
