<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/standardUncertaintySN> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#double> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ucumCode> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ucumCode> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "<p><em>ucumCode</em> associates a QUDT unit with its UCUM code (case-sensitive). </p><p>In SHACL the values are derived from specific ucum properties using 'sh:values'.</p>"^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ucumCode> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> "https://ucum.org/ucum.html"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
