<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/ucumCode> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/udunitsCode> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/udunitsCode> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The UDUNITS package supports units of physical quantities. Its C library provides for arithmetic manipulation of units and for conversion of numeric values between compatible units. The package contains an extensive unit database, which is in XML format and user-extendable. The package also contains a command-line utility for investigating units and converting values."^^<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/udunitsCode> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> "https://www.unidata.ucar.edu/software/udunits/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/udunitsCode> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt> .
